---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout categorySelected="home">
  <article>
    <img src="/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="portrait" />

    <p class="content">
      Hello! My name is Sylvie, and this is my website! Right now, it's mostly
      serving as a blog for various stuff that I feel like writing about, but in
      the future, who knows! Anyway, the site is still a work in progress, so
      some parts won't be working 100% properly yet&mdash;that said, it's
      starting to get there. Anyway, thanks for visiting! Odds are, if you are
      looking for something here, I've moved it to the <a href="/articles/"
        >Articles</a
      >
      section. Or maybe, you're looking for stuff in the <a href="photos">Photos</a> section instead? Either way, feel free to look around!
    </p>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
<style lang="scss">
  .portrait {
    display: block;
    width: 18rem;
    margin: auto;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-radius: 100%;
  }
</style>
